# USER.md

Your identity file. Run `/get-started` to create this interactively, or copy this to `USER.md` and fill in manually.

## Identity

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Name | {add name} |
| Email | {add email} |
| Role | {add role} |
| Company | {add company} |
| Persona | {add: founder / sales-leader / sales-manager / ae} |
| Mode | {add: solo / team} |

## Autonomy

What AI can do without asking:

**Bot can do:**
- Research prospects
- Draft outreach
- Update pipeline status
- Create today.md
- Process transcripts

**Bot needs approval:**
- Send emails
- Move deal stages
- Delete anything
- Post to Slack

## Preferences

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
